{"tid":2300172,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【一名經人】香港之死 由此書起 - 羅家聰","createTime":"2020-11-25T09:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T19:31:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3deba0cb4c7c853ebb11457c0dde789aaabf12be","tid":2300172,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:49:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201125/SWC3HAUKYZDCBGXXVEQVAFANQA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201125%2FSWC3HAUKYZDCBGXXVEQVAFANQA%2F&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwoZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=e0aa4f79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201125%2FSWC3HAUKYZDCBGXXVEQVAFANQA%2F&h=830d53c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201125/SWC3HAUKYZDCBGXXVEQVAFANQA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【一名經人】香港之死 由此書起 - 羅家聰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xnPMwOnaPkvQ6Or_NjM1vA6GyGs=/4770x2634/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WFV75RG66NFIVN2IYZOOECCUIU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxnPMwOnaPkvQ6Or_NjM1vA6GyGs%3D%2F4770x2634%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWFV75RG66NFIVN2IYZOOECCUIU.jpg&h=e1688c96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■將明明是香港強稱為大灣區，更重要的政治含義是要毀掉香港，最終消失於歷史。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n六星期前，編輯開題寫《施政報告》，區區題為「施政報告，四大路數」的文末提到，你跟她設定的話題團團轉去討論，就中計了。六周過後，話題設定好了：大灣區。<br />\n<br />\n早已指出，去年一役後，林鄭已成為中共的傀儡、徹底的扯線公仔。連上次《施政報告》臨陣改期她本人也遲遲才知，此乃明確政治訊號，告知你全港人誰是幕後操盤的大佬。不只特區的區長毀了，就連特區也公然毀了。<br />\n<br />\n港人眼中，港澳就是港澳，廣州就是廣州，大甚麼灣區？將本來分開的港深廣澳，不知所謂地合稱大灣區，然後叫港青去大灣區搵食，不禁用香港話講：「你講咩呀？」港青在港搵食不好，要到不知哪處的大灣區再人工減去大截，然後賺錢來養香港頭家？再用香港話講：「搞咩呀？區長嚟㗎？個腦生响邊度？」此等路數，港人不會想到。<br />\n<br />\n身為一區之長，《施政報告》竟是叫香港未來的棟樑離開香港，還以為是賣港賊所想。但若是中共所餵飼的台詞，就言之成理了。要國安、要穩定，後生的當然不能搞搞震。濫捕雖多，但告得入的不多，坐牢的更少；無上街的，腦子卻洗不到，惟有洗血好了。出國讀書或移民始終少數，請君入去機遇處處的大灣區，自是中共首要任務之一。<br />\n<br />\n將明明是香港強稱為大灣區，更重要的政治含義是要毀掉香港，最終消失於歷史。消滅了香港，所有香港的問題自然一併消失，反正香港的中西橋樑角色在被圍被制下已所餘無幾。從中共看，此乃極理性的政治計算。香港之死，就始於這份《施政報告》。<br />\n<br />\n再團團轉報告內裏，都多餘了。那麼倒錢落鹹水海的「明日大嶼」？據說發債搞。哪個笨蛋會借錢予人去填這無底深潭？。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n羅家聰<br />\n<br />\nlawkachung@gmail.com"},{"pid":"3f20bfec27355920ab46847cbb803270c04d9386","tid":2300172,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:51:37.000Z","msg":"老一輩都係叫省港澳<br />\n廣州城、香港地、澳門街<br />\n廣東話讀順口到仆街<br />\n咩野大灣區珠三角都係支那北人亂叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全冇歸屬感"},{"pid":"036d3fa1e5f4a1418bf23f88d4e5631442c588ad","tid":2300172,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T09:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/angry_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a73bd66e3f367fb5be0428cc7365b587190d31d","tid":2300172,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05304dcbb864931f68e6a041585960181c651bc","tid":2300172,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T19:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695f5fd12ae5bb6